enchantment.musuen.laceration.desc: Increases the damage of the weapon but at the cost of the user's life.
enchantment.musuen.skewering.desc: Increases the damage of the trident but at the cost of the user's life.
enchantment.musuen.unearthing.desc: Makes the tool dig in tunnels but at the cost of the user's life.
enchantment.musuen.phasing.desc: Makes the user teleport over a wall but at the cost of the user's life
enchantment.musuen.overcharged.desc: Overcharges tools for increased damage but at the cost of the user's life.
enchantment.musuen.reaching.desc: Increases the reaching distance of the user while using a tool.
enchantment.musuen.pocketed.desc: Adds pockets to leggings to increase the user inventory size.
enchantment.musuen.vein_miner.desc: Makes a tool break also connected blocks of the same type.
enchantment.musuen.attraction.desc: Attracts items on the ground toward the player.
enchantment.musuen.meteority.desc: Increases the maximum flying velocity of the elytra.
enchantment.musuen.wingspan.desc: Inflicts knockback to the entities surrounding the player after landing with the elytra.
enchantment.musuen.alighting.desc: Decreases the fall damage while the elytra are equipped.
enchantment.musuen.telekinesis.desc: Teleports the drops from the killed entities to the player.
enchantment.musuen.moon_jump.desc: Makes the user perform multiple jumps while in mid-air.
enchantment.musuen.long_jump.desc: Makes the user perform longer jumper while sprinting.
enchantment.musuen.demonction.desc: Protects the user against demonic damage.
enchantment.musuen.skyhook.desc: Attaches, with a lace, the user to an arrow shot with a crossbow.
enchantment.musuen.reflection.desc: Makes the shield reflect the projectiles shot towards the player.
enchantment.musuen.shockwave.desc: Makes the shield hit the ground to create a shockwave for damaging and pushing away entities.
enchantment.musuen.coverage.desc: Increases the coverage that the shield provides.
death.attack.demonicEnchanting: %1$s made a bad deal with a demon
